text:

author: Archies  Arck

text:
Last memoir ko censor kr diya tune, aakhir nhi hi visible kiya. Lkin tu to apna banda h, itna apnapan lagta h tere saath. Tere rehne se wing me jaan thi bhai. From licking mangos together to motivating each other, we grew up. Itna active aur sincere ho tm apni life me, I need to learn from you. Wing ka hangout spot tha tere room pe, mast khaane peene ki cheejen, kuuch books, cricket ka samaan, football and what not. Vacation me sab apna samaan tere room me chhor k jaate the. Raat ko tere aur sudhanshu k saath canteen jana hamesha yaad rahega (getting emotional while writing this). Tune bahut motivate kiya h mujhe, bharosa dilaya ki sab sahi ho jayega.
All the best bro, AIM high, apne aap ko underestimate mat krna, bohot aage jayega tu (aakhir achut kisko pasand nahi). Same jagah rahe to milenge fir, trip wagerah pe chalenge, tb tk meet krte h. #VIRTUAL_HUG

text:
Hey buddy, you have always been a true companion in the entire college journey. We did lots of academic and non-academic works together. From our first project in Summer of code,
to the last project (in college), DEFT, our friendship and synergy kept on increasing. Your sincerity and music skills always adored me.
You made me believe that my guitar can actually sound good, when I just brought it ðŸ˜‚.
"Give me some sunshine, Boulevard of broken dreams, californication" and many more tunes, I always love jamming with you. You were the first person I met who was not only interested in listening, but doing something in music.
We were so desperate to play electric guitar, also tried to find one, but hard luck! (ab to kharid liya tune)
And how can I forget the movies on projector, PUBG and playing clash royale on speaker, cricket, football and cards!
You are one good natured guy who always helped me whether it be acads or just regular BTs. Cannot wait to see you soon!
#FRIENDS_FOREVER

PS: Apan kisi trip pe nhi gye h, chalte h jaldi hi (photos bhi leni h).

text:

I will miss those late night philosophical talks, weird theories on random topics, ideas, clash royale and many things jo abhi to nhi yaad, but yad aayegi to miss karunga :p. author: Archies  Arck

text:
I honestly don't remember when we first met, kuch dhundhli si yaaden h, kuch ACA ka mail aaya tha, woh dikhane gaya tha mai tumhe. Mujhe 1st summers se pehle hi aur koi memory yaad hi nhi tmre saath. Moreover I feel like the part where our friendship begun is deleted from my brain.
Mai pehle bohot frustrate hota tha tumse, aur fir kaafi insipre bhi hota tha. Like straight logical baaten krte the tum and I assumed ki samne wala banda samjh jayega, but nhi, tumhe exactly correct sentence sunna hota tha.
Your thought process and way to approach any problem is way out of this world. Fir 2nd year me jab hum roommates bane, tb aur jyada friendship strong ho gayi. Despite of asynch routine, koi ladai nhi hui hamari :lol. Tmre saath reh k kaafi knowledge horizon expand hua h mera and my interest list went on increasing. Saath hi physics par se bharosa bhi uthne laga tha. Canteen me bomber, nutcracker aur philosophical discussion will be missed a lot (woh to hum aage bhi karenge hi), saath hi clash royale, uski alag memories h.

Baaki ab yeh kaafi bara ho gaya h, so lets conclude, warna likhte reh jaunga.
All the best bro, you will definitely achieve what you want in life. "The Matrix" banana h pakke se.
Milte h jaldi hi!
#VIRTUAL_HUG
